claim.claim-text:
A method for displaying a dynamic icon, characterized in that, the method comprises:
receiving an icon display instruction;
obtaining a dynamic icon resource pack of an icon to be displayed based on the icon display instruction;
analyzing the dynamic icon resource pack to obtain an icon resource information and a dynamic description information;
generating a dynamic icon based on the icon resource information and the dynamic description information; and
displaying the dynamic icon.

A device for displaying a dynamic icon, characterized in that, the device comprises:
a display instruction receiving unit configured to receive an icon display instruction;
a resource pack obtaining unit configured to obtain a dynamic icon resource pack of an icon to be displayed based on the icon display instruction;
a resource pack analyzing unit configured to analyze the dynamic icon resource pack to obtain an icon resource information and a dynamic description information;
a dynamic icon generating unit configured to generate a dynamic icon based on the icon resource information and the dynamic description information; and
a dynamic icon displaying unit configured to display the dynamic icon.
